metadata.description: Bunny Ice Creams is the sweetest collection of 8000 randomly generated ice creams. These delicious and joyful NFTs exist to make our world a sweeter and cuter place by benefiting global charities and our NFT artist community. By collecting one of our Bunny ice creams, you’ll be donating to GiveWell and funding an NFT artist’s project. We believe in supporting everyone and growing together.
metadata.name: Bunny Ice Cream #1
